cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper deals with automatic cell image segmentation using convolutional neural networks (CNNs) and focuses on error correction through proofreading. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), which deals with image processing and analysis. The use of CNNs for training the classifiers suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper presents experimental results on different connectomics datasets, which suggests that it may also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia).
